data.value:
- E-Voting using fingerprint is a Graduation project made by MTI student 2021-2022.
- The system purpose is to create a safe voting process using computer technology biometric authintication for safer voting process.
- This system uses ZKTecho 4500 fingerprint scanner to scan the fingerprint.
- Voting process is created by only authorized admins which are responsible for the whole voting process.
